quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  20,65,"Qaloo ya moosa immaan tulqiya wa-imma an nakoona awwala man alqa"
  20,66,"Qala bal alqoo fa-itha hibaluhumwaAAisiyyuhum yukhayyalu ilayhi min sihrihim annahatasAAa"
  20,67,"Faawjasa fee nafsihi kheefatan moosa"
  20,68,"Qulna la takhaf innaka antaal-aAAla"
  20,69,"Waalqi ma fee yameenika talqaf masanaAAoo innama sanaAAoo kaydu sahirinwala yuflihu assahiru haythuata"
  20,70,"Faolqiya assaharatu sujjadanqaloo amanna birabbi haroona wamoosa"
  20,71,"Qala amantum lahu qabla an athanalakum innahu lakabeerukumu allathee AAallamakumu assihrafalaoqattiAAanna aydiyakum waarjulakum min khilafinwalaosallibannakum fee juthooAAi annakhliwalataAAlamunna ayyuna ashaddu AAathaban waabqa"
  20,72,"Qaloo lan nu/thiraka AAala majaana mina albayyinati wallatheefatarana faqdi ma anta qadininnama taqdee hathihi alhayataaddunya"
  20,73,"Inna amanna birabbinaliyaghfira lana khatayana wamaakrahtana AAalayhi mina assihri wallahukhayrun waabqa"
  20,74,"Innahu man ya/ti rabbahu mujriman fa-innalahu jahannama la yamootu feeha wala yahya"
  20,75,"Waman ya/tihi mu/minan qad AAamila assalihatifaola-ika lahumu addarajatu alAAula"
  20,76,"Jannatu AAadnin tajree min tahtihaal-anharu khalideena feeha wathalikajazao man tazakka"
